text: The source adds, “Since Taylor’s been in hiding Kendall’s very much the queen bee these days, so what she says goes for the majority of that group. She’s made it clear that anyone listening or supporting Taylor will be banned from her circle instantly, and the likes of Gigi, Bella and Cara are all doing as they’re told.”
title: Kendall Jenner Tells Friends: Ban Taylor Swift Music Or Else!
